{
  "stem": "3988.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we came-- before the coal mine, you know, going down into the coal mine, they took the lock off.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You slip out the chain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You gave to the kapo, you know, the chain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he gave it to the German, you know, whoever it is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we worked down-- walked down in the coal mine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we worked in the coals, you know, in the coal mines.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was help, you know-- and a Polish guy, he was like the foreman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I mean, he worked in the coal mine, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But he's the one who used the ammunition, you know, where you go in-- to blow up the coals, you know, and everything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he got paid from the general government.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Like, he paid for the city or the state, you know, and he was-- because we couldn't use no ammunition.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, we used to load up the coals on conveyors, after he shoot out the coals.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we used to load on conveyors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to load them on small wagons and push them up to-- on the top, to get on the top to-- and this-- this Polish guy, oh, he was a bastard.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I can say that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the conveyors were running on machines, you knows, motors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, do you see this hear?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, [POLISH], you know, like in Polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, he told me, [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, this is the oil of your father and mother, you know, that use from the machines.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CRYING] I was just praying I hope that someday soon-- you know, something happens to him, you know, and everything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day, sure enough, when we went in, in the mine, we were digging.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
